com.customlbs.library

Class EvaluationParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.customlbs.library.EvaluationParameters
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public final class EvaluationParameters
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable

    Encapsulates parameters for evaluation mode.

    Evaluation mode is only for testing purposes e.g. when you test in an emulator. For debugging the real algorithms use dummy wifi mode instead. Uses the Builder pattern. Set the parameters you are interested in and leave the rest to the default value.
